cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper deals with 3D reconstruction using RGB-D cameras and deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method also involves multi-view fusion, which is related to graphics (cs.GR). The use of machine learning suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
